+# UUID
+
+[![License](https://img.shields.io/github/license/gofrs/uuid.svg)](https://github.com/gofrs/uuid/blob/master/LICENSE)
+[![Build Status](https://travis-ci.org/gofrs/uuid.svg?branch=master)](https://travis-ci.org/gofrs/uuid)
